1 var DATA_TYPES = require('../constants/DataTypes'),
  2   Helpers = require('../utils/Helpers'),
  3   CAS = require('../constants/CASConstants'),
  4   ErrorMessages = require('../constants/ErrorMessages'),
  5   ColumnMetaData = require('../resultset/ColumnMetaData'),
  6   ResultInfo = require('../resultset/ResultInfo');
  7 
  8 module.exports = ExecuteQueryPacket;
  9 
 10 /**
 11  * Constructor
 12  * @param options
 13  * @constructor
 14  */
 15 function ExecuteQueryPacket(options) {
 16   options = options || {};
 17 
 18   this.casInfo = options.casInfo;
 19   this.sql = options.sql;
 20   this.autoCommit = options.autoCommitMode;
 21   this.dbVersion = options.dbVersion;
 22 
 23   this.resultset = '';
 24   this.resultCacheLifetime = 0; //Cache lifetime
 25   this.statementType = null; //
 26   this.bindCount = 0; //Bind count
 27   this.isUpdatable = false; //Is updatable
 28   this.totalTupleCount = 0; //Total nomber of tuples
 29   this.cache_reusable = 0; //Cache reusable
 30   this.resultCount = 0; //Number of results
 31   this.columnCount = 0; //Number of columns
 32   this.infoArray = new ColumnMetaData(); //Column meta data
 33   this.resultInfos = new ResultInfo(); //Result info
 34   this.queryHandle = 0; //Query handle
 35   this.currentTupleCount = 0; //Current number of returned tuples
 36   this.tupleCount = 0; //Number of tuples
 37 
 38   this.responseCode = 0; //Response code
 39   this.errorCode = 0; //Error code
 40   this.errorMsg = ''; //Error message
 41 }
 42 
 43 /**
 44  * Write data
 45  * @param writer
 46  */
 47 ExecuteQueryPacket.prototype.write = function (writer) {
 48   var bufferLength = DATA_TYPES.DATA_LENGTH_SIZEOF + DATA_TYPES.CAS_INFO_SIZE +
 49     DATA_TYPES.BYTE_SIZEOF + DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF + DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF + DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF +
 50     Buffer.byteLength(this.sql) + 1 + DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF + DATA_TYPES.BYTE_SIZEOF +
 51     DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF + DATA_TYPES.BYTE_SIZEOF + DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF + DATA_TYPES.BYTE_SIZEOF +
 52     DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF + DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF + DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF + DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF +
 53     DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF + DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF + DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF + DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF +
 54     DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF + DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF;
 55   var functionCode = CAS.CASFunctionCode.CAS_FC_PREPARE_AND_EXECUTE;
 56 
 57   //Prepare info
 58   writer._writeInt(bufferLength - DATA_TYPES.DATA_LENGTH_SIZEOF - DATA_TYPES.CAS_INFO_SIZE);
 59   writer._writeBytes(DATA_TYPES.CAS_INFO_SIZE, this.casInfo);
 60 
 61   if (this.dbVersion.startsWith('9.0.0')) {
 62     functionCode = CAS.CASFunctionCode900.CAS_FC_PREPARE_AND_EXECUTE;
 63   }
 64   writer._writeByte(functionCode);
 65 
 66   writer._writeInt(DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF);
 67   writer._writeInt(3);// number of CAS args
 68   writer._writeNullTerminatedString(this.sql);//sql string
 69   writer._writeInt(DATA_TYPES.BYTE_SIZEOF);
 70   writer._writeByte(CAS.CCIPrepareOption.CCI_PREPARE_NORMAL); //prepare flag
 71   writer._writeInt(DATA_TYPES.BYTE_SIZEOF);
 72   writer._writeByte(this.autoCommit ? 1 : 0); //autocommit mode
 73 
 74   //Execute info
 75   writer._writeInt(DATA_TYPES.BYTE_SIZEOF);
 76   writer._writeByte(CAS.CCIExecutionOption.CCI_EXEC_QUERY_ALL); //execute flag
 77   writer._writeInt(DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF);
 78   writer._writeInt(0); //max col size;
 79   writer._writeInt(DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF);
 80   writer._writeInt(0); //max row size;
 81   writer._writeInt(0);//NULL
 82   writer._writeInt(2 * DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF); // write cache time
 83   writer._writeInt(0); //seconds
 84   writer._writeInt(0); //useconds
 85   writer._writeInt(DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF);
 86   writer._writeInt(0);//query timeout
 87 
 88   return writer;
 89 };
 90 
 91 /**
 92  * Read data
 93  * @param parser
 94  */
 95 ExecuteQueryPacket.prototype.parse = function (parser) {
 96   var reponseLength = parser._parseInt();
 97   this.casInfo = parser._parseBytes(DATA_TYPES.CAS_INFO_SIZE);
 98 
 99   this.responseCode = parser._parseInt();
100   if (this.responseCode < 0) {
101     this.errorCode = parser._parseInt();
102     this.errorMsg = parser._parseNullTerminatedString(reponseLength - 2 * DATA_TYPES.INT_SIZEOF);
103     if (this.errorMsg.length === 0) {
104       this.errorMsg = Helpers._resolveErrorCode(this.errorCode);
105     }
106   } else {
107     this.queryHandle = this.responseCode;
108     this.resultCacheLifetime = parser._parseInt();
109     this.statementType = parser._parseByte();
110     this.bindCount = parser._parseInt();
111     this.isUpdatable = (parser._parseByte() === 0);
112     this.columnCount = parser._parseInt();
113     this.infoArray = [];
114     for (i = 0; i < this.columnCount; i++) {
115       var info = new ColumnMetaData();
116       info.ColumnType = parser._parseByte();
117       info.scale = parser._parseShort();
118       info.precision = parser._parseInt();
119       var len = parser._parseInt();
120       info.Name = parser._parseNullTerminatedString(len);
121       len = parser._parseInt();
122       info.RealName = parser._parseNullTerminatedString(len);
123       len = parser._parseInt();
124       info.TableName = parser._parseNullTerminatedString(len);
125       info.IsNullable = (parser._parseByte() === 1);
126       len = parser._parseInt();
127       info.DafaultValue = parser._parseNullTerminatedString(len);
128       info.IsAutoIncrement = (parser._parseByte() === 1);
129       info.IsUniqueKey = (parser._parseByte() === 1);
130       info.IsPrimaryKey = (parser._parseByte() === 1);
131       info.IsReverseIndex = (parser._parseByte() === 1);
132       info.IsReverseUnique = (parser._parseByte() === 1);
133       info.IsForeignKey = (parser._parseByte() === 1);
134       info.IsShared = (parser._parseByte() === 1);
135       this.infoArray[i] = info;
136     }
137 
138     this.totalTupleCount = parser._parseInt();
139     this.cache_reusable = parser._parseByte();
140     this.resultCount = parser._parseInt();
141     //read result info
142     for (i = 0; i < this.resultCount; i++) {
143       var resultInfo = new ResultInfo();
144       resultInfo.StmtType = parser._parseByte();
145       resultInfo.ResultCount = parser._parseInt();
146       resultInfo.Oid = parser._parseBytes(DATA_TYPES.OID_SIZEOF);
147       resultInfo.CacheTimeSec = parser._parseInt();
148       resultInfo.CacheTimeUsec = parser._parseInt();
149       this.resultInfos[i] = resultInfo;
150     }
151   }
152 
153   if (this.statementType === CAS.CUBRIDStatementType.CUBRID_STMT_SELECT) {
154     var fetchCode = parser._parseInt();
155     this.tupleCount = parser._parseInt();
156     var columnNames = new Array(this.columnCount);
157     var columnDataTypes = new Array(this.columnCount);
158     var columnValues = new Array(this.tupleCount);
159     for (var i = 0; i < this.columnCount; i++) {
160       columnNames[i] = this.infoArray[i].Name;
161       columnDataTypes[i] = CAS.getCUBRIDDataTypeName(this.infoArray[i].ColumnType);
162     }
163 
164     columnValues = this._getData(parser, this.tupleCount);
165 
166     return JSON.stringify(
167       {
168         ColumnNames     : columnNames,
169         ColumnDataTypes : columnDataTypes,
170         RowsCount       : this.totalTupleCount,
171         ColumnValues    : columnValues
172       }
173     );
174   }
175 
176   return parser;
177 };
178 
179 /**
180  * Get records data from stream
181  * @param parser
182  * @param tupleCount
183  */
184 ExecuteQueryPacket.prototype._getData = function (parser, tupleCount) {
185   var columnValues = new Array(tupleCount);
186   for (var i = 0; i < tupleCount; i++) {
187     columnValues[i] = new Array(this.columnCount);
188     var index = parser._parseInt();
189     var Oid = parser._parseBytes(DATA_TYPES.OID_SIZEOF);
190     for (var j = 0; j < this.columnCount; j++) {
191       var size = parser._parseInt();
192       var val;
193       if (size <= 0) {
194         val = null;
195       } else {
196         var type = CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_NULL;
197 
198         if (this.statementType === CAS.CUBRIDStatementType.CUBRID_STMT_CALL ||
199           this.statementType === CAS.CUBRIDStatementType.CUBRID_STMT_EVALUATE ||
200           this.statementType === CAS.CUBRIDStatementType.CUBRID_STMT_CALL_SP ||
201           this.infoArray[j].ColumnType === CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_NULL) {
202           type = parser._parseByte();
203           size--;
204         } else {
205           type = this.infoArray[j].ColumnType;
206         }
207 
208         val = this._readValue(j, type, size, parser);
209         columnValues[i][j] = val;
210       }
211     }
212   }
213   this.currentTupleCount += tupleCount;
214 
215   return columnValues;
216 };
217 
218 /**
219  * Read column value from stream
220  * @param index
221  * @param type
222  * @param size
223  * @param parser
224  */
225 ExecuteQueryPacket.prototype._readValue = function (index, type, size, parser) {
226   switch (type) {
227     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_CHAR:
228     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_NCHAR:
229     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_STRING:
230     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_VARNCHAR:
231       return parser._parseNullTerminatedString(size);
232 
233     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_SHORT:
234       return parser._parseShort();
235 
236     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_INT:
237       return parser._parseInt();
238 
239     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_BIGINT:
240       return parser._parseLong();
241 
242     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_FLOAT:
243       return parser._parseFloat();
244 
245     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_DOUBLE:
246     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_MONETARY:
247       return parser._parseDouble();
248 
249     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_NUMERIC:
250       return parser._parseNumeric(size);
251 
252     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_DATE:
253       return parser._parseDate();
254 
255     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_TIME:
256       return parser._parseTime();
257 
258     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_DATETIME:
259       return parser._parseDateTime();
260 
261     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_TIMESTAMP:
262       return parser._parseTimeStamp();
263 
264     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_OBJECT:
265       return parser._parseObject();
266 
267     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_BIT:
268     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_VARBIT:
269       return parser._parseBytes(size);
270 
271     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_SET:
272     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_MULTISET:
273     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_SEQUENCE:
274       return parser._parseSequence();
275 
276     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_BLOB:
277       return parser._parseBlob(size);
278 
279     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_CLOB:
280       return parser._parseClob(size);
281 
282     case CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_RESULTSET:
283       return parser._parseResultSet();
284 
285     default:
286       return new Error(ErrorMessages.ERROR_INVALID_DATA_TYPE);
287   }
288 };
